 />\n<br />\n而家仲有黃的揀<br />\n你班的士佬摺撚埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a23f80e3bc7f72c492671c01fefb1a4a03f131d","tid":2050642,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"但uber好濕鳩，抽25%水"},{"pid":"499e0b5b8dd65d5abae2913e8276c5f18e9d6e6a","tid":2050642,"uid":144024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:30:22.000Z","msg":"的士10架有6-7架臭到仆街、污糟到仆街<br />\n遠又唔去、近又嫌近、過海又話唔識路<br />\n全世界都智能電話，用導航好難㗎？點可能仲有唔識路？<br />\n<br />\n一係就成堆車喺度撳app接啲好嘅旗，街邊想搵㗎車都難。<br />\nUber 貴嗰少少，但起碼唔會一上車成陣煙味、汗臭、被拒載"},{"pid":"19eec2e61c4aa6c05ace881eea7d4465324e72df","tid":2050642,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:46:18.000Z","msg":"我只會支持黃的台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算uber都唔會幫襯"}]}